Interface Summary
Parser Interface for the jADT description file parsers.
 

Class Summary
DummyParser A dummy parser that compares its input with a test string and produces a test Doc as its output
StandardParser The standard parse for jADT description files
 

Enum Summary
TokenType The set of token types returned by the tokenizer
 

Exception Summary
